Add capability to bulk edit to allow pre-pending or appending text to text fields. Currently, when you bulk edit a text field, it will wipe out all the existing text. We want to be able to add text to existing field without destroying what was there. This could be at the beginning or end of the existing text. This allows putting in keywords that are useful for searches and other tracking. This should work for custom text fields.

